data.text:
DESCRIPTION

The ACUSON P500 ultrasound system, FROSK edition is an adaptable hand-carried system engineered for point-of-care imaging.

The ACUSON P500 FROSK delivers sophisticated technologies from across the portfolio to ensure unprecedented image quality, plunkability, and smart workflow all in a compact notebook format. This new platform based on Siemens pioneering technologies will give users organization and flexibility to grow into the future.
